About Dialogic

Dialogic is a leading cloud-optimized solutions provider for real-time communications media, applications, and infrastructure to service providers, enterprises, and developers around the globe. Based in Parsippany, NJ with offices worldwide, Dialogic helps 48 of the world’s top 50 mobile operators, and nearly 3,000 application developers build and deploy on agile networks.

For more information on the communications solutions built on Dialogic® technology, visit https://www.dialogic.com/solutions.

Specialties

Telecom Equipment and Software, Media Servers, Session Border Controllers, Optimization, Network Congestion Solutions, Application Development, UC for Service Providers, Network Infrastructure Solutions, Video Gateways, Contact Center Transformation
